body:
### Motivation

Right now, broker-stats gives persistent/non-persistent topic-stats under the `persistent` topic section. We need them in separate section to manage them operationally.

### Modifications

Add non-persistent topic under separate section.

### Result

Broker-stats will show non-persistent topic in separate section.
```
{
    "sample/standalone/ns2": {
        "0x00000000_0xffffffff": {
            "persistent": {
                "persistent://sample/standalone/ns2/tp3": {
                    "publishers": [],
                    "replication": {},
                    "subscriptions": {},
                    "producerCount": 0,
                    "averageMsgSize": 0.0,
                    "msgRateIn": 0.0,
                    "msgRateOut": 0.0,
                    "msgThroughputIn": 0.0,
                    "msgThroughputOut": 0.0,
                    "storageSize": 0,
                    "pendingAddEntriesCount": 0
                }
            },
 "non-persistent": {
                "non-persistent://sample/standalone/ns2/t2": {
                    "publishers": [],
                    "replication": {},
                    "subscriptions": {},
                    "producerCount": 0,
                    "averageMsgSize": 0.0,
                    "msgRateIn": 0.0,
                    "msgRateOut": 0.0,
                    "msgThroughputIn": 0.0,
                    "msgThroughputOut": 0.0
                }
            }
        }
    },
```
